# API Documentation

## Authentication
- Handled via Firebase Authentication (JWT-based).

## Endpoints

### Health
`GET /api/health`
- Returns `{ status: 'ok' }`

### Classes
- `GET /api/classes` → list all classes
- `POST /api/classes` → create new class

### Gemini Suggestion
- `POST /api/gemini/suggest-schedule`
  - Body: `{ "classes": [...], "faculty": [...] }`
  - Returns AI-generated timetable

### Notifications
- `POST /api/register-token` → store device token
- `POST /api/notifications/send` → send notification (admin only)

